description: A searchable, web-based tool for accessing data on AUCD training programs, projects, activities, and products. Includes data on the University Center for Excellence in Developmental Disabilities (UCEDD) and Leadership Education in Neurodevelopmental and related Disabilities (LEND) programs.

publisher.name: Administration for Children and Families, Department of Health & Human Services

title: The Association of University Centers on Disabilities (AUCD) Network National Information and Reporting System (NIRS)
